System76 Keyboard Switcher
Supported models: [oryp2-ess, oryp4, oryp5, oryp6] : [serw11, serw12] : [darp5, darp6]
Credits: David Jordan, Cassidy James Blaede, Aaron Honeycutt, Nathanael Anderson
License: GPLv3

